{"vv41:0.1":"Vimanavatthu ","vv41:0.2":"Itthivimana ","vv41:0.3":"Manjitthakavagga ","vv41:0.4":"3. Nagavimanavatthu ","vv41:1.1":"“Alankata manikancanacitam, ","vv41:1.2":"Sovannajalacitam mahantam; ","vv41:1.3":"Abhiruyha gajavaram sukappitam, ","vv41:1.4":"Idhagama vehayasam antalikkhe. ","vv41:2.1":"Nagassa dantesu duvesu nimmita, ","vv41:2.2":"Acchodaka paduminiyo suphulla; ","vv41:2.3":"Padumesu ca turiyagana pabhijjare, ","vv41:2.4":"Ima ca naccanti manoharayo. ","vv41:3.1":"Deviddhipattasi mahanubhave, ","vv41:3.2":"Manussabhuta kimakasi punnam; ","vv41:3.3":"Kenasi evam jalitanubhava, ","vv41:3.4":"Vanno ca te sabbadisa pabhasati”ti. ","vv41:4.1":"“Baranasiyam upasankamitva, ","vv41:4.2":"Buddhassaham vatthayugam adasim; ","vv41:4.3":"Padani vanditva chama nisidim, ","vv41:4.4":"Vitta caham anjalikam akasim. ","vv41:5.1":"Buddho ca me kancanasannibhattaco, ","vv41:5.2":"Adesayi samudayadukkhaniccatam; ","vv41:5.3":"Asankhatam dukkhanirodhasassatam, ","vv41:5.4":"Maggam adesayi yato vijanisam. ","vv41:6.1":"Appayuki kalakata tato cuta, ","vv41:6.2":"Upapanna tidasaganam yasassini; ","vv41:6.3":"Sakkassaham annatara pajapati, ","vv41:6.4":"Yasuttara nama disasu vissuta”ti. ","vv41:7.1":"Nagavimanam tatiyam. "}